PPTEval 18 , 19 , 20 , 21 , 22 18 , 19 , 20 , 21 , 22 18,19,20,21,2218,19,20,21,22 23 
Algorithm 1 Slides Clustering Algorithm
    Input: Similarity matrix of slides \(S \in \mathbb{R}^{N \times N}\),
    similarity threshold \(\theta\)
    Initialize: \(C \leftarrow \emptyset\)
    while \(\max (S) \geq \theta\) do
        \((i, j) \leftarrow \arg \max (S) \quad \triangleright\) Find the most
    similar slide pair
        if \(\exists c_{k} \in C\) such that \(\left(i \in c_{k} \vee j \in c_{k}\right)\)
    then
            \(c_{k} \leftarrow c_{k} \cup\{i, j\} \triangleright\) Merge into existing
    cluster
        else
            \(c_{\text {new }} \leftarrow\{i, j\} \quad \triangleright\) Create new cluster
            \(C \leftarrow C \cup\left\{c_{\text {new }}\right\}\)
        end if
        Update \(S\) :
            \(S[:, i] \leftarrow 0, S[i,:] \leftarrow 0\)
            \(S[:, j] \leftarrow 0, S[j,:] \leftarrow 0\)
    end while
    Return: \(C\)
